Lifecycle methods -->a which automatically triggered during certain phase

Mounting-->whenever we refresh the page ui(class and functional component) for first time is called  mounting for the first time each time we refresh our page it gets mounted
when we search for something the daata is mounted or displayed on screen
constructor , render method will be called for first time

updating-->when we update state variable of class or functional component that componenent only will be re-rendered again is updating

unmounting-->removing /unrendering ui from rendering in conditional rendering

these are all valid for for class based component not for functional based

we use bootstrap for js similarly we can use bootstrap and react material ui for react for design and responsive purpose

custom component-->user written copmponent(counter etc)

we passs data from parent to child component using props,but to pass data from child to  parent 